'''埃弗勒斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Everest'''}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[布朗縣_(堪薩斯州)|布朗縣]]的城市。[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]中該城市人口有284人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=April 9, 2012|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
由於此地有鐵路建設通過，約在1882年於此地設立埃弗勒斯<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA601#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Embracing Events, Institutions, Industries, Counties, Cities, Towns, Prominent Persons, Etc. | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=601 | access-date=2016-03-15 | archive-date=2014-07-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701031835/http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA601#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA149#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=149 | access-date=2016-03-15 | archive-date=2014-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706194148/http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA149#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。城市名稱以擔任{{le|聯合太平洋鐵路中部支線|Central Branch Union Pacific Railroad}}的律師、[[堪萨斯州参议院|堪萨斯州参议院]]議員亞倫·S·埃弗勒斯（Aaron S. Everest）中校命名以茲紀念<ref name=Rydjord>{{cite book|last=Rydjord|first=John|title=Kansas Place-Names|url=https://archive.org/details/kansasplacenames0000rydj|year=1972|publisher=University of Oklahoma Press, Norman|page=[https://archive.org/details/kansasplacenames0000rydj/page/455 455]|isbn=0-8061-0994-7}}</ref>。

==地理==
埃弗勒斯坐落在北緯39度40分36秒、西經95度25分31秒（亦可表示成39.676743°，-95.425269°）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積{{convert|0.26|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，全境為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

